data.description:
Created in 2004, Monster Mini Golf has been setting the standard for excellent Family Entertainment.
Over the years, we have focused on fine-tuning and proper growth. Now with 30+ franchised locations across the US and Canada, we have become the leader in indoor blacklight family entertainment.
Our space-efficient venues consist of, an 18-hole Custom designed blacklight Mini Golf course, state-of-the-art arcade, and Posh Birthday Party & Event rooms with optional Laser Maze, Laser Tag, Bowling & Virtual Reality.  
Each venue is uniquely designed, filled with witty relatable local pop culture artwork, interactive fun animated monsters, surrounded by upbeat music broadcasting from an on-course, DJ hosted radio station. We're a socially-distanced safe, affordable and fun concept that appeals to humans of ALL ages !

In March of 2012, Monster Mini Golf opened the first co-brand location in Las Vegas with the Rock Band KISS. We hold a KISS license and are the first company to open a venture of this nature with the legendary Rock band. 

Dec 2017: Our 2nd Las Vegas location opened, (licensed through CBS) Twilight Zone by Monster Mini Golf opened at Bally's Hotel & Casino.

Our Concept is fun for all ages. Our model is simple and  our business is never dull!
